<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>فَصْلٌ <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>* فَقَول <span class="c2">(٢)</span> أَصْحَابِنَا وَغَيْرهمْ: <span class="c1">"الْمَذْهَب كَذَا"</span>:<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَدْ يَكُونُ:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>- بِنَصِّ الْإمَامِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>- أَوْ بِإِيمَائِهِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- أَوْ بِتَخْرِيجِهِمْ ذَلِكَ، وَاسْتِنْبَاطِهِمْ مِنْ قَوْلِهِ أَوْ تَعْلِيلِهِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">* وَقَولهُمْ:</span> <span class="c1">"عَلَى الأصَحِّ"</span>،<span class="c5"> أَوِ:</span> <span class="c1">"الصَّحِيح"</span>،<span class="c5"> أَوِ:</span> <span class="c1">"الظَّاهِرِ"</span>،<span class="c5"> أَوِ:</span> <span class="c1">"الأَظْهَرِ"</span>،<span class="c5"> أَوِ:</span> <span class="c1">"الْمَشْهُورِ"</span>،<span class="c5"> أَوِ:</span> <span class="c1">"الْأشْهَرِ"</span>،<span class="c5"> أَوِ:</span> <span class="c1">"الْأقْوَى"</span>،<span class="c5"> أَوِ:</span> <span class="c1">"الأقْيَسِ"</span>:<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">فَقَدْ يَكُونُ:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>- عَنِ الْإِمَامِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>- أَوْ بَعْضِ أَصْحَابِهِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">* ثُمَّ:</span> <span class="c1">"الأصَحُّ عَنِ الإِمَامِ، أَوِ الأصْحَابِ"</span>:<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>- قَدْ يَكُونُ شُهْرَةً <span class="c2">(٣)</span>.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- وَقَدْ يَكُونُ نَقْلًا.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) تُنظر هذه المصطلحات في (الرعاية): ١/ ٢٧، و (المسودة): ٢/ ٩٤٧، و (الإنصاف): ١/ ٦، و (المعونة): ١١/ ٥٨٨، و (مصطلحات الفقه الحنبليّ): ٥٣.<br>(٢) في (ب): قول.<br>(٣) من (أ) و (ص) و (ج)، وفي (ب): بشهرته.</p> </div>